      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must cover the operating envelope (flow rate 3–8 L/min, speed 1500–3500 RPM) relevant to CPB clinical use.",
      "rationale": "FDA validation dataset spans 2–6 L/min and 2000–3500 RPM, covering the primary CPB operating envelope. Geometric fidelity of the FDA generic pump to clinical CPB pumps is documented in the COU requirement narrative."
    },
