      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form selection (SST k-omega turbulence, power-law hemolysis model) must be justified by literature precedent; formal model-form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected based on published benchmark performance for rotating machinery. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is the established standard for CFD hemolysis prediction. Literature justification documented; formal model-form UQ deferred per MRL 2 scope."
    },
