      "acceptanceCriteria": "Nominal input values (fluid properties, hemolysis model constants) must be documented with sources; formal sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "All model input values documented with literature or experimental sources. Hemolysis model constants from Giersiepen et al. 1990 as per community standard. Formal input sensitivity analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
