      "acceptanceCriteria": "FDA benchmark dataset sample characterization is accepted as sufficient; independent sample variability study not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump experimental dataset provides standardized test samples with documented fluid preparation procedures. Sample variability characterization from FDA protocol accepted at MRL 2 without additional independent study."
    },
