    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model capability to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump within the CPB clinical use envelope. The model is accepted for submission in support of Class II 510(k) regulatory decision-making for CPB hemolysis risk assessment.",
